1) In the file `pom.xml` replace the following placeholders with actual values:

		$PROJECT_GROUP_ID$
		$PROJECT_ARTIFACT_ID$
		$PROJECT_VERSION$
		$PROJECT_NAME$
		$REPO_OWNER$
		$REPO_NAME$

2) In the file `.github/workflows-template/perform-release.yaml` replace the following placeholders with actual values:

		$REPO_OWNER$
		$REPO_NAME$
		$BINTRAY_USERNAME$

3) In the file `pom.xml` add the information in the out-commented sections (or remove them).

4) Add a new package with the name `$REPO_NAME$` under Bintray -> $REPO_OWNER$ -> repositories -> maven-repo.

5) Add the following secrets under GitHub -> Project -> Settings -> Secrets:

		PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN_GITHUB
		BINTRAY_API_KEY

   The `PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN_GITHUB` must have the full repo scope and the full packages scope.
   The `BINTRAY_API_KEY` must belong to the above mentioned `$BINTRAY_USERNAME$`.

6) Rename the directory `.github/workflows-template` to `.github/workflows`.

7) Afterwards this `FIRST STEPS` file can be deleted.

8) Commit and push the changes. You are ready to go ...
